name: Nina Phoria
desc: I couldnâ€™t believe how beautiful and spacious the place looked- I actually considered taking it off the market and moving back in! I have no doubt that the staging was a major reason I got multiple offers over asking within 24 hours, and resulted in me getting thousands of dollars more than I would have if the place was empty! I would recommend you and your associates to anyone looking to sell.

name: Patrick Johns
desc: Ines, Principal of Envision Redesign, is outstanding. She has such an eye for design, layout, spatial options and an understanding of how to capture the attention of the client or buyer. She's a wonderful person to work with, has thorough knowledge and experience with new construction and pre-existing homes.

name: Chloe
desc: When potential buyers walk into the house they are able to see the house in its fullest potential, an important aspect that can sometimes be a struggle for potential buyers if the house is vacant or poorly staged. The homes by Envision Redesign are smartly designed, with interesting but clean color schemes and attention to detail most designers cannot attain.
